text: Rock Hill may refer to: * Rock Hill, Georgia, an unincorporated community * Rock Hill, Indiana, an unincorporated community * Rock Hill, Louisiana, an unincorporated community * Rock Hill, Missouri, small city in Missouri * Rock Hill, New York, hamlet in New York * Rock Hill (Herkimer County, New York), an elevation in Herkimer County, New York * Rock Hill, South Carolina, fourth largest city in South Carolina * The Aaron Copland House, a National Historic Landmark in Cortlandt Manor, New York, also known as Rock Hill ==See also== * Rockhill (disambiguation) * Rocky Hill (disambiguation) * Rocky Gap, Virginia * Rockville (disambiguation)
title: Rock Hill
